          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Veterans Securing Schools Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Omnibus Crime Control and Safe Streets Act of 1968 to broaden the definition of &quot;school resource officer&quot; for purposes of the Community Oriented Policing Services program to include a veteran who is hired by a state or local agency to serve as a school resource officer.</p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2018-03-06T05:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
        </item>
